          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1189395780" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8630545660800626631">Maureen Johnson used to be &quot;an author I really want to check out.&quot; Now, she is a kick-ass author whose books I must own.<br/><br/>Bermudez Triangle tackles serious issues with wit, grit and humor. Characters are true and they make real mistakes with actions and reactions honestly and unapologetically portrayed. The dialogue is spot-on, as is the spontaneity unique to the young. <br/><br/>This was a quick, compelling and captivating read and I&apos;m sure the start of a whole new obsession.<br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText8630545660800626631" style="display:none">Maureen Johnson used to be "an author I really want to check out." Now, she is a kick-ass author whose books I must own.<br /><br />Bermudez Triangle tackles serious issues with wit, grit and humor. Characters are true and they make real mistakes with actions and reactions honestly and unapologetically portrayed. The dialogue is spot-on, as is the spontaneity unique to the young. <br /><br />This was a quick, compelling and captivating read and I'm sure the start of a whole new obsession.<br /><br /></span>
